Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.48,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:03.83,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:08.84,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:15.76,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:20.26,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.18,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.94,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:30.15,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.15,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:36.07,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:41.33,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:47.04,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:50.25,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.08,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.88,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:02:00.22,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:07.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\pos(960,6)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.64,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:11.27,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.44,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
